org.apache.beam.sdk.extensions.sql.meta.provider.hcatalog

Class HCatalogTableProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.sdk.extensions.sql.meta.provider.hcatalog.HCatalogTableProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, TableProvider

    public class HCatalogTableProvider
extends java.lang.Object
implements TableProvider, java.io.Serializable
    Table provider that represents a schema stored in Hive Metastore.

    Supports only 'db.table' format at the moment, does not support 'catalog.db.table'.

    Delegates to sub-providers to get the actual table.

    If only the table name is provided, then 'db' is assumed to be 'default'.
